            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Verisk Analytics Inc(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:VRSK:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/VRSK\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">VRSK-US</a>)截至台北時間17日00:33股價下跌12.38美元，報231.61美元，跌幅5.07%，成交量799,256（股），盤中最高價242.05美元、最低價231.61美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.61%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.68%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.69%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.38%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Verisk Analytics Inc(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:VRSK:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/VRSK\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">VRSK-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+0.21%</li> <li>近 1 月：-4.35%</li> <li>近 3 月：-18.71%</li> <li>近 6 月：-17.31%</li> <li>今年以來：-10.76%</li></ul></section></main>",
